public class GenericDataAccessRenditionImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements GenericDataAccess

A custom data source implementation for Rendition View and Entity Objects. This class implements the contracts required by the AbstractGenericViewObject and AbstractGenericEntityObject.

update

public GenericRowData update(GenericRowData data)

Ignore calls to update the row. The Content Server does not support updates to renditions. This method is not expected to get called. However, if it is called, it will do nothing.
